Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.93,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(238,214,248,204)\bord0\c&H000000&\fn@DFGangBiW2-B5\frz275.341\frx350\fry2\pos(248,204)}你在校期间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.93,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(190,189,200,179)\bord0\c&H000000&\fn@DFGangBiW2-B5\frz275.341\frx350\fry2\pos(200,179)}为了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.93,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(129,261,139,251)\bord0\c&H000000&\fn@DFGangBiW2-B5\frz275.341\frx350\fry2\pos(139,251)}而努力奋战到底
